2010", shape=ellipse, URL="RFC5402.html", target="_top", tooltip="This document explains the rules and procedures for utilizing compression (RFC 3274) within an Internet EDI (Electronic Data Interchange) 'AS' message, as defined in RFCs 3335, 4130, and 4823.  This document is not an Internet Standards Track specification; it is published for informational purposes."];
